content.detailedDescription: Me and two friends were hanging out at pensacola beach close to where the cross landmark was on some sand dunes we were standing at waters edge on gulf of mexico. the gulf was like a lake that night no waves or wind. one of my friends spotted it first. the friend that spotted it we had both gone through radar school together in the at navy great lakes illinois the other friend was in a local technical school who is now deceased. the object was a large spherical ball of light traveling parallel on the main beach road heading due east. my friend that spotted it said "dudes check it out a ufo. so we started jumping up and down hollering and waving at it like welcome to earth. within about two seconds the object changed course towards up then became stationary directly above us maybe ten feet over our heads. the object did not make any noise what so ever. we all looked up at it absolutely amazed. my radar school buddy then shouted run and we took off running from it. the other friend who is now deceased said he also claimed  saw an object go down in the water in the gulf not to far from us. we regrouped in the sand dunes then my radar friend spotted it continuing on its eastward course close to where the lighted up main part of pensacola beach is. the strange thing was that this time when we spotted it was just a black sphere and there were no lights on it like it wanted to remain hidden going over the lighted up part of the beach. it traveled right next to the pensacola beach water tank and it was several times larger than the spherical shape of the water tank. then it faded off in the distance. end of sighting. on a humorous note only then did we open and chug down the bottle of sangria wine we had with us :) lucky we didn't get abducted that night

June 17th 2015 12:15am 

i was leaving my driveway for a walk as usual with my cat, but this time he wouldn't come with me, he looked paranoid with his ears back crouched at my window. so i continued walking, when i heard the fence rattle coming from the far side of my building, i thought it might have been kids trying to hop the 10 ft barbwire fence to cut threw the field.So i walked towards where the noise was, it was so dark i couldn't really see anything at 1st, i pulled out my camera and tried to turn my flash light on, but it wouldn't work, i then switch to my camera thinking i could use the flash, i took one pic but the flash didn't work, that's when i noticed what i was looking at bcuz this 2 ft alien pop'd out of the shadows from the corner and i snapp'd another picture, i wasn't really sure what i was looking at it was so alien to me but he just stood there on 2 feet looking at me, so i started walking backwards very slowly taking the last picture, he then jump'd the barbwire 10ft fence in one quick motion, i wasn't sure if my eyes were playing tricks or not, i then started to questioned what i just witnessed ..An animal? when it landed it leaped in one motion about 25-30ft and then whistled 5 notes like a scale going up and down. i then was convinced it was exactly what i thought i was looking at, continuing walking away from my building,not wanting to be in an in closed area i thought i would just go for a long walk and hope he was gone when i seen an alien ufo to the west that at 1st was the size of a star but quickly grew so i thought it was coming for me so i ran and jump'd to grab the sewer grate across from the stop sign, bcuz of it's speed i knew it would be 3-4 seconds if that, as i was an inch from grabbing the sewer a beam of light shot out and caught me in the air, my body inches from the street, and i just couldn't reach the sewer i then started to get pulled backwards and up  i guess to avoid the power lines instead of straight up. when the bean shot out, my fingers were able to scoop out some cement leaving a 3 foot hand imprint drag mark in the cement, i have no memory of being on board and actually i didn't remember seeing the ship or the drag mark until 3 months after while i was trying to figure out, how what i thought was an hours walk ,really was 6 hours, i don't remember being returned i just remember seeing the sun coming up as i was around the block walking home, and b4 i went in i had stopp'd right where i was taken because to the east there was the strangest looking cloud it looked like a face smoking so i took a quick video of it then went inside. i thought since i was only gone for an hour maybe 2 at most that i must have took the pics of the alien around 3-4am but when i checked the time on the picture it said 12:15am? this had me stumped cuz i didnt remember being abducted, it felt like one continuous walk after taking his picture, then like i said b4 i was out side reenacting everything when i got to the stop sign and remembered the ship then i remembered the sewer walked over to it and nearly puked when i seen my drag mark, also i have a faint vision of seeing the alien that jumped the fence standing on my neighbors driveway as i was pulled up.  here's a link to the face in the sky video -https://www.Youtube.Com/watch?V=cktsoiougrs also i included to compare the 3rd picture with the same daytime picture, you can see the aliens head is obscuring the horizontal chair leg,  i've added some enhanced copies of pic 2 black and white zoomed in with the aliens left eye highlighted, and pic 3 i added 2 enhanced to see him better, the last cement pic is where the alien stood when i was being pulled up and i'm pretty sure he made this mark ,i didn't have time to take a pic of the ship sorry enjoy

content.detailedDescription:
It was a long time ago, when i was about eight to eight and a half years old. my parents and i saw three domed shape flying saucers as we called them.  they came over the mountain ridge about a mile and a half from where we lived. we were on our way home from grandma's. they came over on the right side of the car and hovered on the ridge of the mountain. there was no sound, and then after a short while they just disappeared.  it was broad daylight. mom and dad just kept talking about them and wondered if they were part of the mass hysteria going on about the people in manchester nh.  

after that i didn't think about it until i was 13 years old, it happened again down town winchester nh, except there was only one shinny uf0 that descended from the sky at night. quiet a few people saw that one but everyone was told it was a weather balloon. most people including myself wanted to believe it was a weather balloon.

in 1975-76 i had to undergo surgery on my neck.  when the neurosurgeon and orthopedic surgeon went through my mouth to remove the odontoid tip they retrieved what looked like a bb. we all wondered how that got into the tissue in the back of my throat. i had often wondered about that. i thought about the time my little brother shot my sister in the lip with his bb gun, and could he have hit me with one.

for years, when i took airplane trips they would wand me and it seemed as if i was wearing metal in my lower leg. it wasn't until i needed an mri a few months ago that a piece of metal in the lower left leg appeared. we were looking for something in the right leg. the mri machine attendants asked me if i had any mental on because the machine was showing an alarm that i had metal on. we looked and felt through the cloth on pant leg. we couldn't find anything. when the findings came back there was a piece of metal about 8mm long. no one can explain it. my doctor, probably because he is a naturopath thought we should just leave it alone. if it has been there all these years it can stay there is what i was also feeling until i began to feel invaded again.  i asked my doctor to set me up with a surgeon to get it out of me. the surgeon didn't want to do the operation because it was imbedded too deep. he suggested an orthopedic surgeon. we set up an appointment for that, then i watched a documentary about mufon.  i stopped everything. because i wanted someone i felt i could trust to remove it while i am awake and see what it is myself. so now i am waiting to see what will happen next.  will mufon help me to a doctor they trust to get this out of me.
content.summary: They came over the mountain and hovered for a few moments and disappeard, no sound no trails in the sky.

content.detailedDescription: I was walking to work, it was quarter to seven in the morning and very dark, as i was walking down the side of the railway,  i became a little scared and started looking behind me and walked faster to get to the street that was more lit up,  as i turned into the street, i looked up for some reason, i don't know why and they were all up there. i knew exactly what i was looking at. i was stunned, i felt like i had just won the lottery, then scared,  i felt happy then i felt i wanted to cry,  loads of different emotions but at the same time still in shock, very difficult to explain. the sky was clear and a large fleet of circles,  no noise, looked like they had individual clouds under them.  they were moving slowly ahead. one moved away from the formation on the left really quickly and another came in from the right,  to join the formation. i looked for clouds, birds,  planes it was not any of those things.  i know exactly what i saw and iv never been the same, the strange thing is,  it never entered my head to get my phone and take a photo which is just not like me, i was just so shocked that i knew what was above me. then i became aware that i was walking in the middle of the road thinking i was going to be late for work. i never saw them dissappear, i dont remember what happened to them only that i was just walking to work in shock. iv never been able to walk down that road at that time since. i have seen many things in the sky over the years that cannot be explained but this i know for fact were a fleet of what people call crafts from another planet and i cannot stop thinking about it
content.summary: On way to work, many circles above me, on the left one moved fast,  on the right one moved into fleet.

content.detailedDescription:
Im from ohio, but i visited a girl in malta for new years eve and stayed for a week. on new years eve we went out and did the usual: visited a coue clubs, drank danced etc. she tends to sleep late and we didnt even get to bed til around dawn. i woke up first, not unusual. i got up, and had a cigarette, but i wanted to be outside and she has 3 balconies so i went out on the one by her kitchen. the other is for the dog and cats, and the third is accessed thru the besroom and i didnt want to wake her. im smoking on the balcony because im in a new place and enjoyed being outside and seeing something besides ohio. i looked at the horizon and the sky, just sort of taking in this experience. as i looked in the sky i saw a black dot. i think as humans we jave the ability to sort of judge distance feom seeing cwrtain things all our lives.. we see planes and bkrds in the sky every day. i saw the black dot and knew it was higher than a bird, and higher than a plane. and i first thought "bird? plane?" and honestly wanted it to be explained as either. it was too high. and slow, but moving slowly from left to right. so small that i would look away and have to focus on the general region where id seen it a second before, but there it was. afyer three or four times looking away and refocusing, i started seeing white orbs in my direct vision. not in the sky but in my vision. to the point where i at first swatted at them because i thought it was gnats or something. but as id try to focus on one to determine what it was, theyd disappear from my direct vision and reappear in the sides of my vision. and they happened a bit more as id try to focus back on the black dot i was watching.
i began to feel confused because i couldnt make sense of this, and i thought "am i still drunk?". but i am a drinker, i handle my alcohol quite well and know my limits. i wasnt hung over and was not still intoxicated. 
arou!D the time i begin to wonder if my phone camera will even focus on something so small, i realise my friend is awake and i see her in the kitchen. i feel confused and like i shouldn't tell her because i feel like its crazy and inexplicable. a buzzing sound starts happening. her condo is on the top floor of the building she lives in, and it sounded electrical..Like wires. and it sounded like it was coming from the roof. i looked back to try amd find the dot but it was gone or behind clouds.
i went inside, still feeling odd. she started to make coffee and the power cut out. i dont know the technical layout of her place, bit she had to leave and go to the bottom floor to reset a breaker or something. as soon as she shut the door,i had an incoming phonecall from something that wasnt even a phone number: 5171#32. i didnt answer because i was a little freaked out now, i managed to screenshot the call after it appeared, and immediately my phone died.
i felt strange about the whole thing, not exciytd to tell anyone. she had to reset the power several times and we had had any problems before, or after that. i didnt tell her til a couple days later.
as she made coffee after we got the power back, i went back out for another smoke, and saw an identical dot originating in the same spot where id seen the first amd i just went back inside.
content.summary: Very high elevation. slow steady path. no bird. no plane. too high. orbs in vision after initial observation. strange phonecall. power outage. buzzing.

content.detailedDescription: We as a group were moved to travel 20 miles to a remote location familiar to each of us. why we went there. why we went out of the way of our original destination. i feel like we were led there. as we parked on a remote road to enjoy some beer and good bud. we saw it. a bright object hovering over a house in the distance. occupants of the house yelling at it. it begins to move. i notice another similar object. we are being "scanned". i can feel it. as both crafts move behind us we realize. this is unusual. no sound. low speed bright changing in intensity. light. like the sun. but smaller. we start the van. missing time. next thing i remember we are traveling down a road a mile away from original location. we are being followed. guided. there were 4-5 objects at different distances. the light. as it passed thru the trees created a laser effect. broad fields of light with great intensity. as we are led out of the area. the object comes closer. 35 ft away. 35 feet up. size of two vans. a half sphere. as me and my friend observed. windows began to open like there were layers to the craft. like eye lids kind of. as the outer layer moved it revealed windows. one at a time. the fourth window revealed a head. like greys. it looked at us. they were so close. it was so real. we witnessed the same thing. in disbelief we searched for reason. helicopter?  no noise. the face. at that moment another craft appeared on the horizon. many lights i said. oh crap. it's the mother ship. it was an airplane. 737. southwest. as it flew over. i remember thinking. the noise. we could here it long before it passed over head. but these other objects. no noise. at all.  complete silence not even a hum. we left the area in a state of shock. rationalizing what we had seen. they were looking for something out there. when i told my mother. she stated. maybe they were looking for something. how did she know what i was thinking. she went on to say. maybe they are looking for something here that we have in great abundance that to them is sacred. then it dawned on me.  crystals. there are many limestone caves that produce enormous crystals some the size of small cars. having done some research i know now the significance. quartz crystal. it takes centuries to produce. it requires curtain elements and ideal environments to produce. i had a close encounter of the third kind. i feel strongly that one of my friends was abducted. her behavior.  the fear. she crawled under the bench seat in my friends work van. in her good clothes. she crawled under the seat and would not come out til we got a safe distance away.
content.summary: I had a close encounter of the third kind in the presence of two other individuals. there was missing time. unusual behavior by friends. possible abduction.  the light. so white. so bright. yet you could look at it. like lasers but rays of light.

content.detailedDescription: I was at home on my patio on a nice sunny, slightly hazy day and had been working in the yard and my back was hurting so i got into my zero gravity reclining chair to relax for a minute. i wasn't there probably a minute,looking straight up in the air because i was in a completely reclined position,and i saw what looked like an airliner with no wings or tailpiece,just the tube flying directly overhead and lower than an airliner that isn't coming in to land or taking off,probably under a mile high. it appeared white in color and about the same length as a 757. it was traveling to the northeast at a good rate of speed,but not unusually fast i would say. i watch the sky alot and live several miles from louisville international airport and rarely see planes traveling in this direction. i was kind of stunned when i first saw it because i could see the craft very well,yet no sign of wings. my camera was right next to me because i always try to be ready for my next sighting,but i was so fixated on trying to find wings and if it was worthy of a photo that i hesitated before i grabbed it. it traveled about 10-15 seconds  and then it was about 15 degrees from strait up and the sun hit it and reflected off and still no wings. the only explanation i could come up with was the wings could have been painted a dark color that blended with the sky and weren't reflective so they weren't visible. i decided i better take a photo at this point so maybe i could zoom in later to see it better. i just pulled this up this morning 1/23/16 for the first time along with another sighting i had in december,and decided to send it in and see what you all think.
content.summary: Saw what appeared to be a flying tube fly directly overhead

content.detailedDescription: It was roughly 5.20pm friday afternoon when i received a phone call from my friend lee morgans, so i rolled a cigarette and made my way out into my back garden with the dog as i normally do. so as i remember it, i stopped lee half way through conversation and said there’s one mate high in the sky! a ufo i said! i do believe the reply was something like, really another one? (not being the first time seeing a ufo) so i am describing where in the sky the object is located by describing the stars to lee because orion’s belt & the moon was to my right from where i was standing at the time, as the object passes the moon lee said to me i can see it too mate! i said what? you can see that from where you are and his reply was yes! he is out walking his dog at this time, later checking on google earth the distance is 5 miles between us so i am impressed with this fact! as the object is silently gliding toward my house (still quite high estimated 1000ft) i keep saying please flash! & are you seeing this “lee yeah its flashing’’. not knowing if its flashing at us or me or just flashing randomly?  i’m thinking to myself and speaking out loud there is no pattern to the flashing so it must be flashing to us mate. so about a minute or two into watching this metallic round object flashing random or at us and gliding silently towards my house getting closer & closer at an estimated speed of about ten mph lee is saying the same thing! flash. when the object is more or less over my house lee said i have to go help my girlfriend with the shopping so we ended the call, i can imagine the confused look on her face when turning up to see lee staring into the sky! ha-ha. i then thought i should be getting this on camera so i ran into my house trying to get past the dog because she thinks i’m out there to play, running towards her while still looking into the sky myself and it looks like its fazing in and out now? heart racing, i come back out with my canon legria hfr606 hd camcorder, so while looking in the sky again where i thought the solid object should be but it seems to have disappeared? how bazar considering it seemed solid just now? (repeating to myself please flash) but couldn’t see anything? so i continue to record anyway and end up swearing on camera out of disappointment of missing the whole encounter! while moving the camera all around the area looking for the object i pull the camera down slowly & suddenly the object reappears in and out! with my eyes it looked like it flashed at me again like before but not as bright as when it was higher in the sky so while looking at the footage after i not only realize it’s not flashing like the last time we saw it flash but fazing in and out, wow i’m so glad i didn’t stop recording now because i caught the last fazing in and out on film!
content.summary: Craft appeared metallic & solid! flashing bright white at us before dematerializing above the houses, i seem to have recorded something completely different to what was seen by us both in the sky that flashed at us twice. weird!
